Well-experienced doctors, great care for patients.
Easy to communicate, prompt response on WhatsApp

Dr explained the problem carefully and helps to correct the problem and rectify the problem after seeing my blood report 
Thanks

The doctor tries to explain everything with ease and elegance. 
******** ********* *** ***  ***** *** ******* 
Seeing Doctor Madhumati Kumra since ages
Very talented 🙏🙏

Efficient Doctor, explained my problem so well and the treatment also. The staff wasVery Well behaved . . The clinic was neat and clean. The doctor was friendly and made me feel comfortable and relaxed. Treatment was very satisfying.

At the very outset Dr. Kumra makes you feel at ease and comfortable. She explains the problem and diagnosis with clarity and uses easy to understand terminology. 
Besides taking care of the problematic teeth, she advises on preventive measures, maintenance and hygiene of your teeth. This is a very unique aspect of Dr Kumra's practice. It is very rare that a doctor spends time for such advice. 
Dr Kundra is very soft spoken and gentle which made me feel comfortable and confident that I had come to the right place. 
Last but not the least , her clinic is spotlessly clean with very high standard of hygiene.  And her staff is very well trained for their respective assignments.

I have been coming to the clinic for the past 3-4 years. Everytime i visit from the UK, i always come to the clinic for a checkup and teeth whitening. I prefer it more than UK dental care system. The clinic is very supportive and client friendly and they ensure that their client is getting the best treatment. The doctor is very sweet and polite, she explains everything in detail before carrying forward any kind of procedure. The clinic is not only well maintained with good staff *** ********* *** **** ** *** ** *** **** * **** **** ***

Dr. Madhu is very meticulous and she focuses on all the details. She explains the dental problem and the line of treatment well. The treatment is very well planned. She sees to it that the patient gets the best treatment and care.  ***  ** ****** ************  ** ********* ***** ******* ** ****** ***********
I will highly recommend her.

Very humble & comforting. Explained the health issue completely. 
Very patient & the best at her work.

I visited Dr.Madhumani for problem with my ongoing treatment for root canal with another Dentist. The moment i landed at her clinic, the place had a very soothing ambience. I found the clinic to very professionally run. The staff was very courteous. Dr. Kumra very patiently understood my situation & through technology could easily explain the problem that i was going through & the way forward. She took time out to explain to me the systems & processes that are being followed in her clinic on sterilization all the instruments used in her clinic.I would highly recommend her to my family & friends.

Dr Kumra has extended a very professional service on my first visit with consecutive follow ups. I was highly impressed by her state of the art clinic. I went in for a root canal and tooth inflammation. Her experience & expertise took care of treating my tooth ache in the short time I had on my short visit to India -- Her taking out time to explain what the procedure was to be & what is to follow, gave me great assurance to come back, each time I visit Delhi, for my dental care visit. My dental work has been taken care off, much to my great satisfaction. Thank you Dr. Kumra, see you in March of 2016 !

I had gone for a root canal to Ms. Kumra. I had heard horror stories of root canal procedures and the painful stories and I was extremely terrified. To top it all I have a fear of needles so the fear factor was really high. Ms. Kumra patiently explained the procedure, took care of my fears and was very gentle throughout. The procedure was done very nicely and I must confess it was nothing like the horror stories I had heard! It was almost painless. I would highly recommend Ms. Kumra. A big thank you!

She was ever smiling, described the steps simultaneously while carrying on procedure. Very confident. Teaching the staff nurse and Doctors simultaneously. Taking response of the patient throughout while carrying on procedure, making the patient(myself) at ease and comfortable.

Wonderful experience !!

Got my scaling and polishing procedure done by Dr. Utkarsha under the supervision of Dr. Kumra. She ensured that I was comfortable during the procedure and it was completely painless. They also educated me about the correct ways to maintain my oral hygiene for a healthier mouth in the long term.

I had a good experience. The doctor is competent and pleasant. For a dental treatment she was very reassuring and I have planned to come again for further treatment. I would recommend her highly. The clinic is also very clean and uncluttered with soothing music and nice aroma. Overall a great experience!

My daughter is 3yrs old and unfortunately she has to go through root canal. As we all know it's very painful but with the help of  doctors and the staff it become a bit easy. Dr. Madhumani is such a nice lady and she has loads of patience to handle kids. So far I'm very happy and satisfy from her services

Every time I visit Dr. Kumra, I get to see her efficiency and expertise. Which is terrific.

She is also a very hard task master. Her juniors keep getting stern instructions from her on their methods. This is how they get better in their work. She is a not just an excellent dental practitioner; she is also a wonderful teacher. As a teacher myself, I should probably use some of her methods on my students…

Excellent and pleasant experience as always! Dr. Kumra is my go to dentist and her clinic is super neat, clean and spacious and all covid protocols are being strictly followed.

My family and I only trust her and her clinic especially during these unprecendented times. 

Her staff is also super nice and friendly. Would highly recommend Smayate Dental Clinic and Dr. Kumra to everyone!

had 3 teeth extracted and at the same time implants put in  . Got this done in the middle of the second wave of the covid pendamic.  It was amazing that all care was taken to keep me and the doctors and the assistants safe from exposure to any thing. Whats more is that ive recovered from the surgery and can't wait to get the teeth put in. Thank you Dr Kumra, for your patience and the excellent care.

Dr Madhumani is a very kind *** ************* ******* She makes her patients very comfortable. Her staff is also friendly and well trained. I have visited many dentists but so far this was my best experience. She also educates her patients to maintain their dental hygiene. Thank you doctor, gratitude 🙏🏽

I had gone for my dental cleaning to Smayate Dental Clinic. My entire family goes to this clinic for their dental needs. I was super happy with the procedure. Additionally, Dr. Madhumani also explained my dental condition in detail and took a lot of care to explain me what I need to do to take care of my teeth. I would highly recommend this clinic to everyone.

Dr Kumra has an excellent eye aesthetics & a gentle hand. Her understanding of global best practices and explaining patients the need for a prescribed procedure gives one a lot of confidence. I am very happy with the treatment.....coming to Smayate's calm environment takes the stress out of a dental visit !!!

Dr. Kumra did a  very thorough checkup and explained the issues very clearly so I could take an decision about my treatment. She discussed the entire treatment and plan very patiently. Since my treatment requires implants  and therefore expensive she also shared how it could be staged so that I could get it done in bits. I was in pain a couple of times due to the extent of damage in the teeth and gums I had to reach out to her and she responded immediately and I got relief soon after the treatment was complete.

I always come to Dr. Madhumani  for my dental problems as I feel comfortable in her diagnosis and treatment. Earlier, my parents used to come to her for several years due to the faith in her diagnosis and treatment. My sister also visits her.

What I found as a refreshing change was the education given to me about my problem  by  the doctor and this was accompanied by a presentation of different options available to me for treatment, simple practices to improve the level of oral hygiene. All this and a patient friendly soothing ambience makes this a pleasantly different  experience.

I a student visited Smayate Dental Clinic for Orthodontic treatment.Being welcomed into the a warm welcome and gentle smile on Dr Madhu's face,feeling both excited and nervous on getting braces .She has been a very great ,comforting and a trustable doctor to be.The staff is very welcoming and polite.I am sure my treatment will lead to a beautiful smile at the end of it.

I a Medical Travel Consultant visited Smayate Dental Clinic for dental treatment. Very professional and efficient. Dr Kumra is extremely competent and deft and puts her patients well being as a top most priority .I would recommend her clinic and expertise to everyone I know.

I have been a long time patient of Dr Kumra .Specifically I consult Dr Kumra for my dental care because I find her to be meticulous and thorough in prognosis and dental work.I am completely satisfied. Also very good ambience in the clinic-clean air and ac,and soft music in the background.

I am an advocate and I am seeing Dr Kumra for over 15 years.After visiting her first time ,I never felt like seeing any other Dentist.She is very proficient in her work and always keeps patients comfort in her mind.The present clinic at Gk 1 has excellent facilities. She is very courteous and keep her appointments on time.Satisfied with her professional approval.

Wonderful office .Very attentive and I loved not waiting to be seen.Dr Kumra has been my dentist since my childhood ,she is very professional ,detailed and meticulous.Her staff and her clinic is very organized and caring.They make going to the dentists a very pleasant experience.

My appointment was very efficient. Dr Kumra explained everything .She was telling me how to improve my dental hygiene also.I was very pleased with the service I got and the staff were very friendly.The clinic was also well presented .I would recommend this clinic to others.

My experience with Dr. Kumra has been a 100% breeze! As most of us, I have a dentist chair scare and so much so, that I ignored her advise for almost 24 months but dragged my feet during my visit to India this time, as I could see how chronic the situation was. Dr. Kumra is not only highly knowledgeable and experiences, but extremely calm and easy to talk to. Don't think any further if you want a caring & expert hand for your dental woes!!
Have been seeing her for a number of years & have had lot of work done & a few implants. Very happy with her work. I come from Canada to get this done as am very satisfied with her work.

Very courteous staff and no waiting time .
The doctor is very gentle and very professional 
Overall very satisfied
Been coming to Dr Kumra for 10+ years. Very satisfied with services. Professional and attentive staff

Absolutely magical experience with Smayate. The process was as painless as it could be. The facility provided was top notch along with the staff. And under the expertise and experience of Dr. Madhumani Kumra i felt completely safe.
Doctor was very friendly, and explained the treatment perfectly! A must visit for anyone looking for aesthetic dental procedures.
Dr Kumra is a thorough professional when it came to various  dental procedures ,without compromising the comfort level of her patient.

Excellent* ** ***** ** **** *********** *** ******** **** *** ***** She is caring and does not over prescribe unnessarily along with being sensitive and aesthetic in her  choices. I am very happy with the work she  has done for me over the years. I came to her 10 years ago with a painful bridge that i had got made by a reputed  dentist.  *** ***** ** ********* and it is still going strong. Last year, I had to see a NYC dental surgeon for an emergency procedure and he immediately noticed and complemented this  bridge, saying it shows exceptional craft and intelligence. The premesis is also Super clean and hygienic and the entire team works well together.

Its alwaye pleasent and a wonderful experience whenever I visit , its not just a usual dental visit you get to know a lot of information to keep you mouth healthy. Dr kumra has experience like no other I would highly reccomend.

Dr.Kumra has always been informative and fulfilling as a doctor. She delivered on time and cost. And has always proceed great solutions that are feasible for patient physically as well as financially. Great service.

Dr. Kumra is an excellent doctor **** ******** proficient and professional in her handling of the patients. 
I certainly would recommend her to my family members and friends.
Great doctor. Loved her holistic approach. Dr. Kumra doesn't give you a short term solution and doesn't believe in patchwork.
Great doctor **** ********* ******* highly recommended. Extremely near place & staff also very helpful

Amazing clinic hygiene
Staff and Doctor are extremely experienced
No fear now to go to a dental clinic
Excellent my experience was very good. Doctor Madhu was excellent,she explained everything very well. Her work was meticulous and she took great care. I would recommend her.
Dr. Kumra is fantastic at her work, and generous with her time. The clinic follows impeccable hygiene, and all the staff are trained wel, friendly and efficient.
Dr was very nice person. She described me the reason behind the toothache and what she had done  for its remedy.
Very pleasant...explained the issue well ... efficient & very hygienic... all protocols for COVID being followed

** ***** ** *** **** **** **  am a satisfied patient 5 years plus ..Implant.. crowns .. filings .. now with all work done .. routine maintenance is all that is required and my oral health is great Tks Doc
No words....but I want to say only best👍All staff are friendly and helpful. Dentist is very polite in nature and knowledgeable
I visited there for my son's tooth filling. I'm very much satisfied with the procedure she had done. I would love to recommend to all my friends.

Dr Madhumani is very professional, sincere and give desired comfort to her patient. I have had four sittings and I look forward to address my dental issues or my family to her. 
She was kind enough to take my treatment during lockdown, Covid times which is very rare. 
I wish her great success and happiness

Doctor Kumra is extremely kind and very patient. I cried for over an hour the day I got to know I had to get a root canal treatment done but she assured me that it won't hurt and the treatment actually was very smooth. She's an excellent doctor with a very pretty smile..

I have always been scared to visit dentists.. But I was made so comfortable there that I forgot about the whole mindset of having pain rather enjoyed how I got to know about my own tooth and oral hygiene..The staff was really friendly and took care of safety in Corona times.. The doctor was patient enough to hear me out..In all.. Wonderful experience..

We go a long way, she is very precise and good at what she does.I have great confidence  with her as my dentist.
We do share some pleasantries  inspite her busy schedule.
Her chamber is very welcoming,  polite staff and ambience is lovely.Lots of plants and it's well maintained and artistic.

It is her in-depth manner of explaining the he problem that anyone can easily understand. She did the complete treatment which required just two visits. I have been to dentists before but this was a completely different experience. She spent so much time on explaining the issue and treating it. I would recommend everyone to do visit her. You would get a detailed analysis of your current status for all your teeth. Don't wait for the problem to occur, identify the problem before it occurs.

I would like to thank an amazing dentist and her staff. The friendly staff and the zen like atmosphere of Smayate dental clinic made me feel welcome and comfortable. Dr. Kumra is extremely professional, very thorough, puts me at ease, explains what needs to be done and provides valuable advice. Her team is excellent. There is no other dentist that I would go to. I will  highly recommend Dr Kumra and her staff to all.
Dr.Kumra is a very good dentist and she has been my dentist for many years now. I would recommend her to everyone that bi know.
Now I feel better after  my treatment[cleaning] I m so glad to came here ,you r so experiecal Dr thank u so much  Dr Madhumani kumra.I m waiting to see u again as soon.

I visited at smayate dental clinic .Dr madhumani kumara is  very good doctor.
Excellent analysis and implementation, professionally handled always!
*** ***** ** * ************* ****** *** her clinic is equipped with latest equipment and offers best treatment possible.

It was great as always the doctor and staff are very caring will recommend the clinic to all my friends and family .........

Extremely satisfied with the treatment.The professional and personal touch of the clinic is exemplary.Dr Kumra with a midas touch gives every patient assurance and a ray of hope.Thanks for the whole experience.

I have been a patient at this clinic since its inception and have been satisfied with the treatment of the doctors and the attention of the staff.The standards of cleanliness and hygiene are very high.

The whole experience of dental care has been made very easy and painless at Smayate. Dr Madhu specially is not only excellent in her skillsvas a dentist but also vey gentle and sensitive to the patients needs.
I know Dr  madhumani kumra  since last twenty years.Me and my family are very satisfied with the treatment.She is very patient,modern as well as follows ethical dental protocols.

Excellent care and extremely professional.Trustworthy and when I am in Smayate Dental Clinic I know I am in the best hands.
I came to Smayate Dental Clinic for the first time .I really appreciate the work of Dr Madhumani Kumra and her team.I was very satisfied with the treatment.

I came first time to  Smayate Dental Clinic for implant.At first I was very scared but then as Dr Kumra started doing the procedure everything went on well and I finally I was very happy after implant was placed.Service was quite good.

Very personal and caring atmosphere created by most gentle doctor I ever came across. Always feel like recommending more of my friends and family near by, to get the same excellent experience that I receive through Madhu mam.
Very transparent and comfortable experience. Doctor was very personable and forthcoming with her approach and advice.

Recently I visited Smayate Dental Clinic and got filling done in one of my anterior tooth.It appeared very natural and life like.Very precise and detailed work was done.Place very clean and beautiful. Staff is very helpful.

Madhu is very patient,  professional and an expert at her job.  She explains the issue, gives great advice and helps you take a considered decision. 

Her hand is very soft too
It was good, very kind and explained how to take care of my teeth post the procedure.
Excellent hygiene & treatment service . Good attention and ambience. Treatment well explained before & after.
The doctor is very clear and precise and understands the problem , I have to visit again as the healing will take time

I can say....this is the first doctor who make me feel so comfortable ...i did my treatment with out fear... i get out of my weakness... And i am so happy to SMILE now.... THANKYOU DOCTOR
It felt good and understanding. Ma'am was cooperative and very detailed with her analysis and treatment options.
Dr Kumra is a gentle and patient dentist… both essentials for this type of work! Her experience and knowledge I rely on! And would recommend her without doubt!
It was my second visit. Experience during the first visit for RCT was so good that I did not even look for other options this time. As usual, neat and hygienic environment. Good care...

Dr Kumra, has done a few root canals in my mouth and her work is impeccable. She takes the time to explain and gives you honest advice for future care of your oral health.  I'm deeply satisfied by her diagnosis and treatment.

The experience was good.  Tooth extraction was satisfactory. 
At other visits to the clinic too I have had similar experiences. The staff is competent and helpful
The doctor really helped us in understanding the procedure. We are really satisfied with the services provided to us at the clinic.

I was pleased with the explanation by the Doctor.
I now await a full report and the cost from her before commencing the treatment.
Thank you.
she was on time...was courteous with me...was able to identify my problem..did immediate treatment and relieved me from immense tooth pain.

It was a great experience . It didn't felt like any professional service. I will recommend them always above anyone else
All Covid-19 safety measures were followed. I was explained the process of treatment. Didn't experience pain. I value Dr. Kumra's experience and knowledge.

Would highly recommend

Dr. Kumra is a perfect balance between professionalism and friendliness. She is on top of her job and very through in her procedures. The clinic is well equipped and follows stringent hygiene practices.

Dr. Kumra and her team are talented professionals of high standards who treat their patients with utmost care, respect and patience. Dr. Kumra teats my 82 year old mother as well as me. I highly recommend Dr.Kumra.

Dr Kumra is very friendly and took a lot of time to explain my problem and the treatment she was going to provide.
 She gave a prompt appointment and I did not have to wait. Also, her charges are quite reasonable.
Personal attention doctor gave to  each patient specially to kids.... Her caring attitude.. keep up the good work
For Dental treatment, i only go to Dr. Madhumani Kumra. Her treatment is excellent and there are never follow up complaints.
